  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to built the standard of Chinese Traditional Medicine test for
      Post percutaneous coronary artery intervention and coronary artery bypass graft，also for
      acute coronary syndrome，according to the multi－site、random large sample test.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
